original_title: STARRCAST II: "I Quit" With Magnum TA & Tully Blanchard
overview: Legends Magnum TA and Tully Blanchard made history in their "I Quit" match and set the bar for years to come! Now hear from two of the greatest performers to ever grace the ring on how they made true magic! Hosted by he one and only Tony Schiavone!
title: STARRCAST II: "I Quit" With Magnum TA & Tully Blanchard
